name: my little fish
lyrics:
Dear skinny fish
Listen to me for a while
We have no more tears
No more struggle, no more wine

You're my little fish
Swim to me and take some cheese
Do you still believe
He would come back? He's a freak

And then my fish she says
"I thought he belongs to me
I know I should not mind
I cannot tell lies
He puts me aside"

Fish starts to cry
Other fishes cry and cry.
Fish keeps on crying
"wu wu wu…"

Little baby fish
Listen to me for a while
We have no more tears
No more struggle, no more wine

From now on
From now on
From now on

album.name: 只因當時太緊張
album.name_en: Becoz I Was Too Nervous at That Time
